{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I opened the door, and he saw the negro.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was already in the room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He turned back and walked out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I couldn't look Beaufort in his eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Beaufort was an extremely intelligent, a polyglot, speaking about seven or eight languages well-- with colossal education.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was a very high position.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was a position of a general, lieutenant general, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Equivalent, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "For the negro to get this position, a mulatto, he had to be 20 times as good as a white.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I couldn't look-- when this major walked out, I couldn't look Beaufort in his eyes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Beaufort was a very able guy, very at this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Look, I was in Germany when I was waiting for the migration papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Finally, in December, before Christmas, '47, I got the telegram that the papers are coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "What happened in the meantime, what I knew about it, the position was beside individual permits were called people as a displaced persons going on contract.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But we notice that they don't accept any Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] After a while, we knew that this is not coincidental.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Then I found out what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In the United States was a so-called Jewish Labor Committee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever heard about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "The head of the Jewish Labor Committee was Dubinsky, who was the president of the International Government Workers Association, and senior vice president of American Federation of labor.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The first minister from immigration from Australia was Caldwell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "When Caldwell went first time for overseas trip, his first stop was in United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he got audience with Green, who was the president of the American Federation of Labor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And during this meeting, Dubinsky was present.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Dubinsky later told me the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
